reviewText: Great video on the long pole. Classic Benny Meng. Thank you Benny for making such a great series of videos.

Benny Meng is already a legend for me. He explains things clear and concise, still comprehensive. Wonderful source of information and trustworthy. I like the fact he has also trained outside wing chun, this gives him a much better and balanced view / perspective on wing chun.
A pretty thorough treatment of the long staff, it's going to give me hours of pleasure in learning.
